                  è§£é”å®Œæ•´æŠ¥å‘Š
                </h2>
                <p className="text-muted-foreground">
                  è·å–å…¨éƒ¨æ·±åº¦åˆ†æå†…å®¹
                </p>
              </div>

              <div className="space-y-3 mb-6">
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
                  <span className="text-green-500">âœ“</span>
                  <span className="text-foreground">å®Œæ•´è¿åŠ¿åˆ†æ</span>
                </div>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
                  <span className="text-green-500">âœ“</span>
                  <span className="text-foreground">å¤§è¿æµå¹´è¯¦è§£</span>
                </div>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
                  <span className="text-green-500">âœ“</span>
                  <span className="text-foreground">ä¸ªæ€§åŒ–è¡ŒåŠ¨å»ºè®®</span>
                </div>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
                  <span className="text-green-500">âœ“</span>
                  <span className="text-foreground">é«˜æ¸… AI æµ·æŠ¥</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div className="text-center mb-6">
                <div className="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <span className="text-3xl font-bold text-skill-primary">Â¥19.9</span>
                  <span className="text-muted-foreground line-through">Â¥39.9</span>
                </div>
                <p className="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">
                  é™æ—¶ä¼˜æƒ ï¼Œæ°¸ä¹…ä¿å­˜
                </p>
              </div>

              <button
                onClick={() => {
                  // TODO: Implement payment
                  alert("æ”¯ä»˜åŠŸèƒ½å³å°†ä¸Šçº¿");
                }}
                className="w-full py-3 bg-skill-primary text-white rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-skill-primary/90 transition-colors"
              >
                ç«‹å³è§£é”
              </button>

              <button
                onClick={() => setShowUpgradeModal(false)}
                className="w-full mt-3 py-3 text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"
